24 static inline void
25 g_autoptr_cleanup_generic_gfree (void *p)
26 {
27   void **pp = (void**)p;
28   g_free (*pp);
29 }
30 
31 static inline void
32 g_autoptr_cleanup_gstring_free (GString *string)
33 {
34   if (string)
35     g_string_free (string, TRUE);
36 }
